Class PointLD

java.lang.Object

          bg.x2d.geo.PointLD
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable
public class PointLD
extends Point

Point Long-Double. Implementation of a 2D point that stores its value as a double and allows quick access also as a rounded int or long. Qualifies polymorphically as a Point or Point2D, so it can often be passed to Java2D functions (including AWT/Swing).

Since:
2DX 1.0 (1st Edition)
Author:
Brian Groenke
